attributes.title: Cairngorm Brewery
attributes.description:
Created on February 28, 2010 by leo on Sourcemap.org:

Set up in late 2001 to market the beers of the Tomintoul and Aviemore breweries, which they own.  Ales include Wildcat, Stag, Highland IPA and Trade Winds.  Seasonal ales are brewed
